Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:04.37,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是連前進軌道都無法改變的幾率
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:08.88,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有百分之一就要奮起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:12.71,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟、被「命運」所束縛的人生、不 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:19.39,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我要將它重寫、因為若能看見你和未來 不是最棒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:22.52,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧！我只想在戰鬥中成長 HEY!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:23.35,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,擊穿陰天！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:26.52,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我的烈焰仍舊熊熊燃燒 雷鳴撕裂天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:30.36,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想消除夢魘 看見未來！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:32.86,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,過去、未來、還有如今當下、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:35.82,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我不畏懼過去 現在為了被托付的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:37.20,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吼出我的驕傲!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:43.83,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不想看到眼淚、所以要不斷嘶吼！一直永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:47.83,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會墮落！因為揚起的風會讓我凌駕於命運之上！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:54.21,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,因為身後、有著想要守護的笑容！ 永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:57.72,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,為了彼此！我會揍飛你心中的痛苦！讓悲傷什麼的永遠安息！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:02:01.85,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,832)}無論多少次…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:34.91,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,月光搖曳 我們未來的藍圖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:42.17,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天會實現 描繪明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:46.96,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠不會磨滅 銘記在心中的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:55.77,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,若是無盡的淚水能掩蓋傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:23:04.82,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,那就無需畏懼 再次去相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:13.28,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,向著無邊無際的天空 張開雙臂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:19.12,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不再哭泣 仰望天空中那輪皎月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:24.92,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,即使心存悲傷 也要懷著希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:29.26,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,就算無法回頭 也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:35.93,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,熠熠生輝的夢想 閃耀在探索的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:41.94,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,最寶貴的那份思念 仍舊在延續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:47.73,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,無論哪裏 我們都一起走過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:55.58,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,825)}握住那唯一的心靈之匙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我…都是因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界要終結了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是公主的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都因為那個未來人的算計
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在這裏很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我要留在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留到最後一刻是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狩獵龍的魔法師 滅龍魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把未來托付給他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的 人類是戰勝不了龍的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了守護大家 不當人也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪莎克雷亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾夫哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍蛋！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 你家蛋黃是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 艾爾夫哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個龍蛋是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙生了扔下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子敵人不只有這7頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:19.26,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(640,450)\fad(524,0}基爾柯尼斯的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一頭龍就已經很難對付了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉克薩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都退下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大的交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們對付小的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一人太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們為你掩護 拉克薩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就交給雷神眾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們聽到夏的聲音了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打倒龍 還得是滅龍魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏就交給拉克薩斯和雷神眾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽吉魯去對付其他的龍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的成員對付小型怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要齊心協力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽吉魯 我來當你的後援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 對了還有那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去把逃到百姓那裏去的小型怪獸找出來 引到街外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格 這裏交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去對付其他龍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去幫助沒有滅龍魔法師的協會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏的聲音給了我勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是戰鬥的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是守護同伴的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有感情的劍齒之虎已經終結
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在瑪莎克雷亞背上的傢伙好像在喊著什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們協會沒有滅龍魔法師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好啊 沒有能夠對抗的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼沒有啊 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個時候果然還得我出場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,HI 粗魯的龍先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我治癒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾一邊去 人類
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 就讓你嘗嘗我的迷藏之香好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的鼻子…要不好使了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這個香味到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我腋下的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺如何啊 諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是一夜先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不能動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是多麼的帥不可言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美麗就是我的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼美好的香味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍的嗅覺都很靈敏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 老夫是沒有鼻子的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論過了幾百年 人類都是這麼愚蠢的種族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們退下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都認得這個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽見了 混亂和絕望的悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們滾開 自戀狂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自戀狂？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是失禮的打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是六魔將軍的柯布拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒之滅龍魔法師 為什麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他救了狼狽不堪的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是吹的什麼風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道 美人計也可以奏效麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看著我 帥氣的柯布拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唧唧歪歪的吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心我們你們一起給收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是地獄耳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Men 但是我有疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他應該是在單獨牢房中的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我們竟然會答應傑拉爾的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是被革職還好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把未來創造出來 再擔心以後的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要勇猛過頭去送死啊 多蘭巴爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是要小心啊 拉哈爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大聲幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都聽不見聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛的聲音 埃裏克？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請再向高台方向移動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍稍休息一會兒 就要開始翻山了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃裏克在的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃裏克也在戰鬥呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要大家齊心合力 就沒有辦不到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還未知曉龍之力的恐怖之處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 老夫看看先從哪個傢伙開始吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年輕的姑娘們看上去都很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓咪就當偶爾換個口味了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這些 這些亂七八糟的也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基爾柯尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們交談過的啊 你不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 我要吃了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛的小姑娘啊 就先吃你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的 溫蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們交談過的基爾柯尼斯 是很久以前死去的亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽到夏的話了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能打倒龍的只有滅龍魔法師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在這裏的滅龍魔法師只有你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要振作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定好了 就把你們一起吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的 大家請退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐 請快點把公主帶到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 公主 去這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的和做的 根本就是驢唇不對馬嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 我快吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類確實很美味 但是衣服很難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以先扒了再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盔甲被…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好丟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是不要看過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼悲慘的場景還是第一次見到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不知羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光著身子沒辦法戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太丟人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎重考慮之後 發現男人都不好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人 老夫要吃女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主不能吃 因為他是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 公主不應該是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛是魔法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 所有龍都會使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊 讓衣服消失的魔法什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脫光光了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 是用來剝奪人類尊嚴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用來打倒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用來打倒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒我的魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那個衣服 給我衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 至少給我衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著挺好吃的 我聞我聞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別聞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來挺有嚼勁的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住 手 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 你生氣了？ 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能在我吃掉這個姑娘之前打倒我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臂力強化 耐力強化 附加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得挺愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自不量力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺老橋段又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法飛翔的人類能到達這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是上空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷得身體會變緊變美味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒效果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫蒂 趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:14:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天龍的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 溫蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有效果了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西就交給咱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給你了 哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要打敗基爾柯尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別太得意了 我會連說話的食物一起速度吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來協助 溫蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼砍怎麼砍都會涌上來 像是不會減少一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 艾露莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡娜也說了吧 快去休息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 這裏我們來處理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再衝過來多少次都無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七年的差別不是那麼容易填補的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比大魔斗比武的時候強多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經和未來露西約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能輸給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是會再站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用看到未來的絕望 就死在這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼裸奔啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 別暴走啊 淡定點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是個毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥都太過分了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是暈乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有裸體在空中飛的傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 別看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法 幫你擋一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般都會擋自己的眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 最近的孩子真不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈比 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西成變態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被龍擺了一道 被龍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你這個 是鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是還想再看看咩？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 夏也贏不了那個羅格嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒那回事 那種傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那傢伙確實挺強的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且騎的龍也挺危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍都是那麼兇暴的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龍 岩石龍 連基爾柯尼斯都在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差點就被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被吃掉…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到了好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 戰勝那傢伙的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒完沒了的 越來越多地涌出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大魔斗比武正是預選的落幕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 活躍的地點終於換過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺厲害的啊 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我記住 暮光奧加所屬的冰與火的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫塔金澤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暮光奧加…那些傢伙也參加戰鬥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 別放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅密歐 你是男子漢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵龍棍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 真夠結實的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 和大家走散了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腳…動不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是太逞強了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 艾露莎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡娜也說了吧 快去休息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒法示弱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明知道自己沒那麼強的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你這樣 站起來都拼盡全力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是我多管閒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拉你一把嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米莉安娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個樣子 是玩彩頁攝影嗎？公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是 是緊急事態
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫我準備衣服嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充滿魅力的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說…還在戰鬥中啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 這樣如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:21:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星靈界的流行 哥哥也會高興到哭的一件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候怎樣都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西 我等不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上就換好 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 夏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子換衣服和逛街都是要花時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦 那就之後見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這衣服怎麼回事 穿起來太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為聽說是在戰鬥中 就準備了合適的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太自我中心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢當
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的能順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧 肯定有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有辦法？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 想的主意還真是亂七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要懲罰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也會讓人期待他肯定會有辦法的 夏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是全裸親近的關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的筆記本？ 為什麼在這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撿起來了 就是說裏面寫著公主相當羞恥的秘密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪 為什麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是未來的我的筆記本？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.91,0:24:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 戰勝未來羅格的辦法究竟是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.46,0:24:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這辦法還真是令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.21,0:24:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.62,0:24:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會又是和之前一樣什麼都沒考慮過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼和之前一樣啊 你就是這麼看我的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.30,0:24:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏莫非有謹慎思考過的時候麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.55,0:24:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我也會有過認真思考…應該有…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.55,0:24:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 人對人、龍對龍、人對龍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.35,0:24:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這次有好好考慮過的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.44,0:24:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的麼？

